tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE population_data (
    district_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    city_district VARCHAR(255),
    population_count INT,
    population_growth_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    median_income DECIMAL(10,2)
)

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    demo_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    city_id INT,
    age_group VARCHAR(20),
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    population INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (city_id) REFERENCES cities(city_id)
);

CREATE TABLE growth_trends (
  trend_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  district_id INT NOT NULL,
  year INT NOT NULL,
  growth_rate DECIMAL(5, 2) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (district_id) REFERENCES city_districts(district_id)
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
  demo_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  district_id INT NOT NULL,
  age_group VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
  population_count INT NOT NULL,
  gender VARCHAR(6) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (district_id) REFERENCES city_districts(district_id)
);
